Liono laughs "This was a waste of my time the preds just want someone to Draw 
off the heat." Liono Transforms into his beast mode. Liono looks at hellbeast 
"I'm not the one who got my ass kicked by the newcomers so who really is the 
idiot. So watch your tongue you over grown thunder Lizard or tonight I dine 
on Dragon stew." Liono jumps up the rocks leading to the Jungle." I'll speak 
with my Team the tell you whether or not we work together." Liono Heads 
towards the maximal base and Goes on his intercom All Maximals meet me in the 
war Room now."
